    "name": "步行减肥法",
    "steam_appid": 3305200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras/18556ba0b35a54936ae3edf1acc1a14a.avif?t=1770111082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras_big/18556ba0b35a54936ae3edf1acc1a14a.avif?t=1770111082 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款步行模拟器是一款在家就能轻松锻炼和减肥的工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在行走过程中，会实时显示消耗的卡路里、行走距离、所用时间、场景数量和进度百分比等信息，让你轻松保持动力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras/f9d25b979680635957ccd3ba0348aa41.avif?t=1770111082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras_big/f9d25b979680635957ccd3ba0348aa41.avif?t=1770111082 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >站在电脑前，点击播放时间开始。 伴随着场景播放和脚步声，开始跺脚练习。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果在脚下铺上垫子，您可能会觉得做起来更舒服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做跺脚运动时，双臂要用力摆动，刚开始可能会感觉有点吃力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，随着你的坚持，你的身体会逐渐适应，你也会逐渐开始喜欢上走路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，你会感到一种振奋和希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras/adaffe53f7f9fb65475215ae4f921b45.avif?t=1770111082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras_big/adaffe53f7f9fb65475215ae4f921b45.avif?t=1770111082 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展动力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我一直在为缺乏锻炼和无法保持节食而苦恼，但我决定开发这个模拟器，因为我认为它可以帮助我克服这些问题，让我在家里也能轻松步行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个模拟器是我进行理想步行锻炼的完美工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前，我每天都坚持用这个模拟器进行训练，以促进我的健康。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras/6dea3bdc5bc46c10f63896e738e4bb95.avif?t=1770111082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras_big/6dea3bdc5bc46c10f63896e738e4bb95.avif?t=1770111082 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[夜间恐怖模式］</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您选择了[夜间恐怖模式]，就会播放出具有阴森恐怖的夜间氛围的场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种模式非常适合那些想享受稍微刺激一点的夜间漫步的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras/cb5de86a77d49ee778db26f3efd2968b.avif?t=1770111082\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305200/extras_big/cb5de86a77d49ee778db26f3efd2968b.avif?t=1770111082 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[享受自然］</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视频实时播放，让您欣赏白天、傍晚和夜晚等时区的变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 个不同的美丽自然场景展现在您眼前，为您在漫步过程中提供动力，让您轻松地继续前行。</p>",
